What do you call a penguin in the desert?|Lost
Why are penguins so popular on the Internet?|Because they have Web feet!
How does a penguin build its house?|Igloos it together

missions.title: Case of the Missing Puffles
missions.description:
AUNT ARCTIC, FAMOUS REPORTER FOR
THE CLUB PENGUIN TIMES, IS VERY
UPSET, BECAUSE TWO OF HER PET
PUFFLES ARE MISSING! WILL YOU TAKE
THE CHALLENGE OF RESCUING THEM?

missions.title: G's Secret Mission
missions.description:
G, THE BRILLIANT INVENTOR FOR THE
PENGUIN SECRET AGENCY, NEEDS
YOUR HELP WITH ONE OF HIS NEWEST
PROJECTS. WHAT COULD G BE UP TO
NOW?

missions.title: Case of the Missing Coins
missions.description:
THE COINS FROM THE VAULT IN THE
GIFT SHOP HAVE MYSTERIOUSLY
GONE MISSING. WILL YOU HELP FIND
THEM AND SOLVE THE MYSTERY?

missions.title: Avalanche Rescue
missions.description:
THERE HAS BEEN AN AVALANCHE ON
THE SKI HILL, AND YOUR HELP IS
NEEDED. WILL YOU ANSWER THE CALL?

missions.title: Secret of the Fur
missions.description:
THE MYSTERY OF THE FUR REMAINS
UNSOLVED. WILL YOU HELP G TO
UNRAVEL ITS SECRET?

missions.title: Questions for a Crab
missions.description:
MANY QUESTIONS REMAIN THAT ONLY
A CRAB CAN ANSWER.

missions.title: Clockwork Repairs
missions.description:
THE CLOCK TOWER NEEDS REPAIR, AND
G NEEDS YOUR HELP.  CAN YOU FIX IT
IN TIME?

missions.title: Mysterious Tremors
missions.description:
TERRIBLE TREMORS HAVE BEEN
SHAKING THINGS UP AROUND THE
ISLAND. CAN YOU SOLVE THIS
MYSTERIOUS MENACE?

missions.title: Operation: Spy & Seek
missions.description:
YOU’VE BEEN CONTACTED FOR A
SPECIAL MISSION TO TRACK DOWN
HERBERT. CAN YOU BEAR DOWN ON HIS
LOCATION?

missions.title: Waddle Squad
missions.description:
THE PSA NEEDS YOU FOR A SPECIAL
TEAM MISSION. CAN YOU WORK WELL
WITH OTHERS?

missions.title: The Veggie Villain
missions.description:
ANOTHER INCIDENT HAS BEEN
REPORTED INVOLVING HERBERT P.
BEAR. ARE YOU READY FOR THE BIG
SHOWDOWN?

strings.help_card: If tied, the highest number wins.
strings.help_firsttime_welcome:
Good day grasshopper,
And welcome to the Dojo.
Tell me what you seek.
strings.help_firsttime_tobegin:
To begin training,
You will first require these cards.
Just like real ninja.
strings.help_firsttime_improve:
To increase your rank,
You must compete in matches.
With hard work comes skill.
strings.help_firsttime_areyouready:
Like the autumn leaf,
You must be prepared to learn.
Are you ready now?
strings.help_firsttime_pickacard:
Each turn, both pupils
Pick a card to play. Secret.
Quiet. Like Ninja.
strings.help_firsttime_water:
The peaceful water,
Brings its soothing harmony,
And defeats fire.
strings.help_firsttime_snow:
The white frigid snow,
Brings with it the winter's chill,
And freezes water.
strings.help_firsttime_fire:
Furious fire,
Brings its mighty, scorching heat,
And will melt the snow.
strings.help_firsttime_tie:
When cards are the same,
The match is not yet over.
Highest number wins.
strings.help_firsttime_howtowin:
Much like the Forest,
There are two paths you can walk,
To reach victory.
strings.help_firsttime_winsame:
The first way to win:
Have three cards of the same type,
In different colors.
strings.help_firsttime_windifferent:
The second path is:
To have one of each card type,
In different colors.
strings.help_firsttime_ingamehelp:
If you should forget,
Mouse over the question mark,
And all will be clear.
strings.help_firsttime_joking:
Stand in the Dojo,
Half an hour, very still.
No... wait. Just kidding.
strings.help_firsttime_gainexp:
To become ninja,
You must gain experience,
From winning matches.
strings.help_firsttime_belts:
As you master skills,
I will award you new belts,
Of different colors.
strings.help_firsttime_fightme:
When you are black belt,
You must challenge me and win.
And I'm pretty good.
strings.help_firsttime_ninja:
When you best my skill,
Then you will be true master,
And become ninja.
strings.help_response_whatdoido: What do I do with these?
strings.help_response_howtowin: How do I win a match?
strings.help_response_becomeninja: How do I become a ninja?
strings.help_award_congratulations:
Congratulations!
Much like the fearsome earthquake,
You have rocked the house.
strings.help_award_belt_earned:
Well done. You have earned
%1 for your efforts.
I am proud of you.
strings.help_defeat_sensei_intro:
The gentle lotus,
Cowers before the storm cloud.
But you... you did not.
strings.help_defeat_sensei_kowtows:
Well done, grasshopper.
You have faced my skills, and won.
And proven yourself.
strings.help_defeat_sensei_gift:
Now receive the mark
Of a Card-Jitsu master,
With this ninja mask.
strings.help_defeat_sensei_final:
You may now join us,
In secret ninja hideout.
Congratulations!
strings.menu_description_competition:
Do you wish to play
And compete with another
Student, grasshopper?
strings.menu_description_sensei:
To become ninja,
You must challenge me and win.
But bring your black belt.
strings.menu_description_instructions:
Do you wish to hear
The instructions of the game
Again, grasshopper?

strings.pow_6: When this is scored, discard one Opponent's Fire card.
strings.pow_7: When this is scored, discard one Opponent's Red card.

strings.tour_start_text:
Would you like to become a tour guide, showing new visitors to %1 how to get around?

Here's how it works. We'll give you a quiz of eight questions about %1. If you get at least seven questions correct, you'll get to become a tour guide!
strings.tour_age_text: To ensure experienced tour guides, your penguin must be more than 45 days old before you can apply to become a tour guide.
strings.tour_banned_text: Because there is more than one ban on this account, and this ban happened within the last 30 days, your penguin is not allowed to become a tour guide.
strings.tour_already_text: Check your inventory, you already are a Tour Guide. Look for the Tour Guide Hat.
strings.tour_fail_text:
We're sorry, but you answered too many questions incorrectly.

Thank you for your interest in becoming a tour guide! You can retake the test at any time.
strings.tour_success_text:
You have passed the test! You have proven your knowledge about %1.

Click the button below to receive your free Tour Guide Hat. Then, be sure to read the manual on how to give good tours.
strings.agent_start_text:
We are looking for a few good penguins to
help make %1 the best it can be.
Even though %1 has live moderators,
we need the help of Secret Agent Penguins
to help be our eyes and ears throughout the
%1 world.
strings.agent_age_text: Your penguin must be more than 30 days old to become a secret agent.
strings.agent_already_text: Check your inventory, you already are a Secret Agent
strings.agent_mission_text: As a Secret Agent Penguin, your mission is to:
strings.agent_mission1_text:
Report any players that are using bad language,
being mean, or breaking any of the other rules.
strings.agent_mission2_text:
Help other penguins so they can have the best
experience possible.
strings.agent_mission3_text:
Keep your identity and the identity of other
Secret Agent Penguins a secret.
strings.agent_rewards_text: If you choose to accept this mission:
strings.agent_reward1_text: You will get a spy phone for your penguin.
strings.agent_reward2_text:
You will get access to the Super Secret Agent
Headquarters. This will allow you to hang out
with other agents after a long day of keeping
the peace.
strings.agent_ready_text:
Are you ready to take the challenge
to become a Secret Agent?
strings.agent_done_text:
Your application has been sent to the
%1 Team.

We will check your application and if you are
accepted a Spy Phone will appear in your
inventory the next time you log in.
If not, please try again later.

tour_messages.town: Welcome to the Town Center!|This is often the first place you visit.|If Club Penguin is having a party...|...this room is usually well decorated for it.
tour_messages.coffee: This is the Coffee Shop.|It is one of Club Penguins oldest rooms.|If you go to the bag of beans in the corner...|...you can play the game Bean Counters.
tour_messages.book: Here is the Book Room.|You can read books from the bookshelf here.|You can also play a game called Mancala.|It is a fun game, but difficult to learn.|Read How to Play Mancala before playing...|then play a few games to learn how it works.
tour_messages.dance: Welcome to the Night Club.|This is THE place for dance parties.|That green puffle on the speaker is called the Keeper...|He was gone for a short while recently...|So it's good to have him back!
tour_messages.lounge: This is the second floor of the Night Club.|It is called the Lounge.|It is a great place to rest after dancing.|Also, fun arcade games are found here.
tour_messages.shop: This is the Gift Shop.|You can buy clothes from the monthly catalog.|Colors and backgrounds can be bought as well.|Use coins you have earned from playing games.
tour_messages.village: Here we have the Ski Village.|Here you'll find the Ski Hill and the Ski Lodge...|...and on your right is just an average Everyday Phoning Facility...|...
tour_messages.sport: Welcome to the Sports Shop.|Here, you can buy all sorts of sports equipment.
tour_messages.lodge: The Ski Lodge is a great place to warm up.|Or, you can play Find Four with friends.|You can also go Ice Fishing out the back door.
tour_messages.attic: This is the Lodge Attic.|It has been used to store just about anything!|It also has more Find Four tables.
tour_messages.mtn: Welcome to the Ski Mountain!|This is the place to be if you like to sled.|Sled Racing is very popular.|The easiest course is the Bunny Hill.|The hardest is the Ridge Run.
tour_messages.pet: The Pet Shop is where you can adopt a puffle.|Puffles are animals native to Club Penguin.|They have different colors and personalities.|They all like penguins, and make great pets.
tour_messages.dojo: Here we are in the Dojo.|Learn to become a Ninja with Card-Jitsu.|Train and earn belts to progress.|Only the dedicated will succeed.
tour_messages.dojoext: This is the Courtyard.|It was covered in snow for many moons!|Enter the Dojo and take the path of the Ninja.
tour_messages.dojohide: Welcome to the Ninja Hideout!|Only ninjas have access to this special room.|Here you will find the Martial Artworks catalog...|Where you can get the Amulet.|The Amulet is the key to open the door.
tour_messages.dojofire: Welcome to the Fire Dojo atop the Volcano!|Here ninjas learn to master the element of fire,|by playing Card-Jitsu Fire!|Talk to Sensei over there to learn more!
tour_messages.dojowater: Welcome to the Water Dojo.|At the Waterfall you can earn your Water Suit.|Only the most powerful ninjas will succeed...
tour_messages.pizza: This is the Pizza Parlor.|Come here to order the best pizza.|If you go into the kitchen...|...you can help make pizzas with the Pizzatron.
tour_messages.beach: This is the Beach, home of the Lighthouse.|It is a great place to relax in the sun.|Sometimes you see the pirate ship docked here!
tour_messages.light: This is the Lighthouse...|...the tallest building in Club Penguin.|Take a look at the pictures on the wall...|...or grab a new instrument and perform on stage.|Go upstairs to find the Beacon!
tour_messages.beacon: The Beacon holds the Lighthouse spotlight...|...and a telescope that you can look through.|And if you thought penguins could not fly...|...you should try the Jetpack game on the right.
tour_messages.ship: This is the pirate ship, the Migrator. Arrrr!|Rockhopper sails the seas in this ship.
tour_messages.shiphold: Here is the ship's cargo hold.|This is where Rockhopper sells his rare items.
tour_messages.shipquarters: This is the Captain's Quarters!|Rockhopper spends a lot of time here.|Look at the corkboard for his photos!|Or, grab a friend and hunt for some treasure!
tour_messages.shipnext: Welcome to the Crow's Nest!|What a beautiful view!
tour_messages.dock: Welcome to the Dock.|You can play Hydro-Hopper here.|Take a ride on a tube behind the speedboat.
tour_messages.forts: These Snow Forts are fun for snowball fights.|Click the snowball icon to throw one.|Over there is the Club Penguin clock.|It shows the time in the Club Penguin Time Zone.
tour_messages.rink: Welcome to the Stadium sports fans!|Take part in the action and start a game!|Or grab a snack and watch from the bleachers.|You can buy items for your igloo...|...and sports gear from the booth.
tour_messages.agentlobbymulti: Here we have an average, Everyday Phoning Facility.|Yup, not much to see here.|Nothing suspicious about it at all...|...let's move on.
tour_messages.agentcom: Welcome agents, to the EPF Command Room.|This room is ultra top secret...|...and contains the latest in secret agent technology.|Check out the new Field Ops computer for your orders.
tour_messages.agentlobbysolo: Hmm.... Looks like I'm the only one here.|I can't really give a tour to just myself...|...or can I?|Here we have the Facility. It's pretty empty.
tour_messages.agentvr: This is called the VR room.|VR stands for Virtual Reality.|Here you can see what the old HQ looked like...|...before it was destroyed by a popcorn device.
tour_messages.boiler: This is the Boiler Room.|It gives electricity and heat to Club Penguin.|Here you can read old editions of the newspaper.|It is a great way to learn about Club Penguin.
tour_messages.berg: This is the Iceberg. It is a secret room.|In the distance you can see Club Penguin.|If you want to dive into the ocean depths...|...try out the Aqua Grabber!
tour_messages.cave: Here we have the Cave, which has its own pool.|It also has windows to see underwater.|Wait a moment, and a crab may walk by.
tour_messages.shack: Welcome to the Mine Shack...|Home of the Mine and the Community Garden!|Help water the garden by throwing snowballs...|...into the green bucket.|Beside the beautiful tree is the Recycling Plant...|...where we use garbage to make useful stuff!
tour_messages.mine: Welcome to the Mine...|During recent construction work...|... puffles were seen entering the tunnel...|...and some are now trapped inside.|Over there is the Rescue Squad's base of operations.|They need your help, and fast!
tour_messages.forest: Welcome to the Forest!|Go to the Cove by walking down those stairs...|...or take the top right path to the Mine Shack...|...and help out at the garden.
tour_messages.cove: This is the Cove!|It is a wonderful, secluded spot.|You can go swimming in the shallow water here.|Or, test your surf skill and catch some waves!
tour_messages.boxdimension: Welcome to the Box Dimension.|This mysterious place is the source of all boxes.|Please leave the laws of physics at the door.
tour_messages.cavemine: Here we have the Mine Cave...|Some workers say they've found buried treasure...|So grab a hardhat and start digging!
tour_messages.lake: Wow! This place is the Hidden Lake...|Where did all this treasure come from, I wonder...|And it looks like there's a door under the water...
tour_messages.underwater: BLUB! This place is Underwater...|Look at all the colorful fish and plants! And treasure!|This place sure is unusual...
tour_messages.eco: This is the Recycling Plant!|Throw your recycling into the Recycletron 3000...|...and turn rubbish into useful things!
tour_messages.stage: Here we are at the Stage|This is Ruby and the Ruby...|...a play with more twists than a chocolate pretzel!|A ruby is missing, so look around for clues.|Pick a costume from the trunk and join in!
tour_messages.plaza: There's always something going on at the Plaza!|Check out Ruby and the Ruby at the Stage...|...treat your puffle to a new toy...|...or enjoy the food and music at the Pizza Parlor!
